summary: CONSUMER RENTED A JEEP LAREDO FROM DOLLAR RENT A CAR.  WHILE STOPPED AT A RED LIGHT THE VEHICLE ACCELERATED SUDDENLY.  THE DRIVER ATTEMPTED TO STOP THE VEHICLE BY PRESSING THE BRAKE BUT THEY DID NOT WORK.  AS A RESULT THE VEHICLE MOVED FORWARD  INTO THE INTERSECTION AND COLLIDED WITH A PASSING VEHICLE.  *MR  *NM
